#
# NEWS for R package connectir
#


01-Sept-2011

*   Add option to copy over background brain as an underlay (bg_image.nii.gz) 
    for later analyses when creating subdist directory
*   Add big_add_multiply_scalar function for Y = a*X + b (a and b are scalars)
*   Port creation of gower matrix from R to C++


10-Sept-2011

*   Began switch to using Armadillo in C++ code for linear algebra operations
*   Refactored compute subdist related functions for better memory handling
*   Memory fix for gower matrix creation


12-Sept-2011

*   Refactered mdmr related functions for better memory handling
*   Fixes to compute_subdist related functions

13-Sept-2011

*   Fixes to compute_mdmr related functions
